author: mcnamara
msg: Add support for testing alternative BSF implementations when testing Xalan Java extensions.
Calling the "extensions" target will test Xalan Java extensions using the -new- default implementation,
Jarkata BSF.  Calling "extensions-with-ibm-bsf" will test Xalan Java extensions using the IBM BSF
implementation which has been used in previous releases.
